I used to cut myself just fitting those things, I am surprised you still have all your fingers.  Have to say though I like the idea of it, I always wondered if I got a really big one of those would it be big enough to generate enough to keep car batteries charged.  But I don't have a workshop to build a really big one.  Three times the size of blade.  However, you have proved proof of concept and if I had a big workshop I would be trying to build one.
Any chance you can take it out in a better wind and see just what it can do?
@UCexbu2MieJaSG_rqnCaa5cQ's comment was just so funny and I can just see you running up to him with some wire, a drill and magnets lol.

